    public final class Source

    A model class representing a source in the Android SDK. More detailed information and interaction can be seen at https://stripe.com/docs/api/sources/object?lang=java.

      • getType

        public java.lang.String getType()
        Gets the Source.SourceType of this Source, as one of the enumerated values. If a custom source type has been created, this returns UNKNOWN. To get the raw value of an UNKNOWN type, use getTypeRaw().
        Returns:
        the Source.SourceType of this Source

      • getTypeRaw

        public java.lang.String getTypeRaw()
        Gets the type of this source as a String. If it is a known type, this will return a string equal to the Source.SourceType returned from getType(). This method is not restricted to known types
        Returns:
        the type of this Source as a string
